      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW XIOMARA (2) hit the ground running from a squeeze draw and prominent early but run ended and faded to finish 7th at Geelong in Mix 6/7 FIN company. Should be very hard to beat this time. SUSTAINABLE (1) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 1.5 lengths from Gravity Rush in second (26.62) at Warragul. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Can measure up. DON'T LOOK (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Shepparton behind Rev Oberon (25.87) in a Rank Limit - Restricted Win. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Can measure up.",
